Modification_Detail.description: extracted metadata from PDS3 catalog and modified to comply with PDS4 Information Model

DD_Attribute_Full.name: instrument_id
DD_Attribute_Full.definition: The instrument_id element provides an abbreviated name or acronym which identifies an instrument. Note: The instrument_id is not a unique identifier for a given instrument. Note also that the associated instrument_name element provides the full name of the instrument. Example values: IRTM (for Viking Infrared Thermal Mapper), PWS (for plasma wave spectrometer).
